J. Geils Band: Seth Justman (vocals, keyboards); Stephen Jo Bladd (vocals, percussion); Peter Wolf (vocals); Magic Dick (harmonica); Daniel Klein (bass guitar). J. Geils Band.
 
 
 


Good Bluesy Rock
This album is full of good bluesy rock-not like their later efforts, e.g., Freeze-Frame (which is good on it&#039;s own merits). The last track "Chimes" is a standout. Recommended for fans of this type of Rock and Roll!!
